*> -------------------------------------------------------
*> SEED-LOANS: Create sample loans
*> -------------------------------------------------------
SEED-LOANS.
    DISPLAY "  Creating sample loans..."
    PERFORM BUILD-DATETIME
    OPEN OUTPUT LOANFILE

    *> Alice: car loan $25K
    MOVE 25000 TO WS-PMT-P
    MOVE 8.50  TO WS-PMT-R
    MOVE 60    TO WS-PMT-N
    PERFORM COMPUTE-PMT

    MOVE 200001         TO LOAN-ID
    MOVE 10001          TO LOAN-CUST-ID
    MOVE 100001         TO LOAN-ACCT-ID
    MOVE 25000          TO LOAN-PRINCIPAL
    MOVE 8.50           TO LOAN-RATE
    MOVE 60             TO LOAN-TERM
    MOVE WS-PMT-RESULT TO LOAN-MONTHLY
    MOVE 22000          TO LOAN-BALANCE
    MOVE "ACTIVE"       TO LOAN-STATUS
    MOVE WS-DATETIME-STR TO LOAN-DISB-DATE
    MOVE 6              TO LOAN-PAID-MONTHS
    PERFORM CALC-NEXT-PMT
    MOVE WS-NEXT-PMT-DATE TO LOAN-NEXT-PMT
    MOVE SPACES         TO LOAN-LAST-PMT
    MOVE SPACES         TO LOAN-PAID-DATE
    WRITE LOAN-REC

    *> James: home improvement loan $75K
    MOVE 75000 TO WS-PMT-P
    MOVE 8.50  TO WS-PMT-R
